text: Anne Elizabeth Blateau (born July 28, 1976 in Paris) is a French actress and playwright. == Life == She studied at Sciences Po Paris.Jean-Pierre Thiollet, Hallier Edernellement vôtre, Neva Editions, 2019, p. 60. Her work appeared at the 2008 Saint-Maur Short Film Festival, 2009 Cannes film festival == Filmography == * 2011: Rendez-vous avec un ange of Yves Thomas and Sophie de Daruvar : a boutique patron * 2014: Prêt à tout of Nicolas Cuche : la babysitter * 2019: Jusqu'ici tout va bien of Mohamed Hamidi: Sidonie == References == Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:French actors
